  <!-- EN: Initial approach book-Medicine -->
  <RI_BookA.label>药诀法门书《灵枢百病论》</RI_BookA.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient book made of Qi condensation, the title of which is "Treatise on Febrile diseases".\n\nElixirs Initial approach is not the main medicine, only involves some ancient means of treatment, but the root cause is also inseparable from medicine. The method of refining medicine is the intangible true fire, the heart is the fire storage, the heart has gas, the body into a furnace, through the true fire to strengthen the perception ability, so as to extract the nutrition of medicinal materials, the top pharmacist is able to use the true fire refining reiki, remove Bad part, so as to achieve similar rejuvenation, resurrection of the dead and other mysterious methods. \n\nThis book is by the late Eastern Han Dynasty medical sage Zhang Zhongjing, a collection of his life to learn a book, which contains a large number of diseases detailed explanation and prescription. \n\nNote: Once you have fully studied one Initial approach book, the cultivatior will be bound to that Initial approach and will not be able to learn any other Initial approach! -->
  <RI_BookA.description>一本由灵气凝聚而成的古书，书名写着《灵枢百病论》。\n\n药诀法门专门研究如何将灵气入药，并以各种手段辅助治疗。药诀法门还能将自身肉体变为丹炉，心是火藏，心中有气，通过真火的加持，令灵气带有各种特殊的药力。顶级医师更是能以灵气还原肉体，从而实现类似返老还童等奥妙之法。\n\n注意：一旦完全钻研完一本法门书，修炼者将与这条法门绑定，无法再学习其他法门！</RI_BookA.description>
  <!-- EN: After reading {PARENT_label}, the cultivator{STUDIER_labelShort} takes the Elixirs Initial approach as his cultivation direction! -->
  <RI_BookA.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>阅读了{PARENT_label}后, 修炼者{STUDIER_labelShort}将药诀法门作为了自己的修炼方向！</RI_BookA.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: {PARENT_label} becomes some sparks of Qi and disappears. -->
  <RI_BookA.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterTitle>{PARENT_label}化为点点灵光，消散了。</RI_BookA.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterTitle>
  
  <!-- EN: Skill book-Luminous bomb -->
  <RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.label>通用功法书《白焰雷》</RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.label>
  <!-- EN: A book made up of Qi, titled "Luminous bomb". \n\nThis skill is based on the inner Dan exercises "Qi bullet" and "Cyclone landmine", and is used as the main means of attack by most Free cultivators. Creates an unstable airbomb in your hand, shoots it out, lands and causes a small explosion with considerable force. -->
  <RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.description>一卷由灵气凝聚而成的读物，书名写着《白焰雷》。\n\n此功法基于内丹功法“气弹”和“气旋雷”改进而来，被大多数散修作为主要的攻击手段。在手中制造出一颗不稳定的气弹，然后射出，落地后引发小型爆炸，威力可观。</RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.description>
  <!-- EN: After reading {PARENT_label}, the cultivator {STUDIER_labelShort} learns the "Luminous bomb"! -->
  <RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>阅读了{PARENT_label}后, 修炼者{STUDIER_labelShort}学会了白焰雷！</RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: {PARENT_label} becomes some sparks of Qi and disappears. -->
  <RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterTitle>{PARENT_label}化为点点灵光，消散了。</RI_BookAbility_BombBullet.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterTitle>
  
