  <!-- EN: A book made up of Qi, titled "Invisible".\n\nThis skill is a technique suitable for assassins that creates a special Qi shield around the body. The shield is defenseless and refracts light to achieve an almost invisible effect, especially in the dark. -->
  <RI_BookAbility_Invisible.description>一卷由灵气凝聚而成的读物，书名写着《隐形术》。\n\n隐形术是一种适合刺客的功法，可以在人体周身制造出一层特殊的灵气护盾。护盾没有防御力，可以折射光线，以达到几乎隐形的效果，在黑夜中效果更佳。</RI_BookAbility_Invisible.description>
  <!-- EN: After reading {PARENT_label}, the cultivator {STUDIER_labelShort} learns the "Invisible"! -->
  <RI_BookAbility_Invisible.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>阅读了{PARENT_label}后, 修炼者{STUDIER_labelShort}学会了隐形术！</RI_BookAbility_Invisible.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
