  <!-- EN: Skill book-Wind flying -->
  <RI_BookAbility_QuickJumpWithNosight.label>通用功法书《御风术》</RI_BookAbility_QuickJumpWithNosight.label>
  <!-- EN: A book made up of Qi, titled "Wind flying".\n\nThis skill can make the practitioner spray Qi throughout the body, disturb the air flow, and achieve short distance flight. Most cultivators are quite fond of this exercise, so the quantity is quite large and the price is not high. Advanced practitioners can use Qi quite skillfully, soaring and flipping in the air, while lower practitioners are more likely to use Qi to glide. In any case, the feeling of flying is always exhilarating. -->
  <RI_BookAbility_QuickJumpWithNosight.description>一卷由灵气凝聚而成的读物，书名写着《御风术》。\n\n此功法可以令修炼者在周身喷出灵气，扰动气流，实现短距离飞行。大多数修炼者都相当喜欢这种功法，所以数量颇多，价格也不高。高阶修炼者可以相当娴熟地运用灵气，在空中腾飞翻转，而低阶修炼者更像是利用灵气滑翔。不论如何，飞行的感觉总是令人心旷神怡。</RI_BookAbility_QuickJumpWithNosight.description>
  <!-- EN: After reading {PARENT_label}, the cultivator {STUDIER_labelShort} learns the "Wind flying"! -->
  <RI_BookAbility_QuickJumpWithNosight.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>阅读了{PARENT_label}后, 修炼者{STUDIER_labelShort}学会了御风术！</RI_BookAbility_QuickJumpWithNosight.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: {PARENT_label} becomes some sparks of Qi and disappears. -->
