  <!-- EN: Skill book-Triple slash -->
  <RI_BookAbility_Slash.label>通用功法书《三段斩》</RI_BookAbility_Slash.label>
  <!-- EN: A book made up of Qi, titled "Triple slash".\n\nThis skill is based on the improvement of the boxing technique of the body, condensing the Qi around the arm, turning it into a sharp blade, swinging almost three simultaneous strokes in an instant, which is unpredictable. This technique is often taught by cultivators who prefer melee combat, especially those who are no longer satisfied with a variety of martial arts and thus focus on training the physical body. -->
  <RI_BookAbility_Slash.description>一卷由灵气凝聚而成的读物，书名写着《三段斩》。\n\n此功法基于炼体的拳术改进而来，在手臂周围凝聚灵气，变为锋利的刀刃，在一瞬间挥出几乎是同时的三次斩击，变化莫测。此功法经常被喜好近战的修炼者所学，特别是已经不满足于百般武艺，从而专注于锻炼肉身的武者。</RI_BookAbility_Slash.description>
  <!-- EN: After reading {PARENT_label}, the cultivator {STUDIER_labelShort} learns the "Triple slash"! -->
  <RI_BookAbility_Slash.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>阅读了{PARENT_label}后, 修炼者{STUDIER_labelShort}学会了三段斩！</RI_BookAbility_Slash.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
