  <!-- EN: Initial approach book-Internal pellet -->
  <RI_BookB.label>内丹法门书《性命真经》</RI_BookB.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient book made of Qi condensation, the title of the book written "Internal pellet Scriptures" \n\nThe Internal pellet initial approach is the ancestor of all initial approach, and countless exercises and Qi skills have evolved from the Internal pellet. Qi circulates in the body along a fixed path, so that the body gradually adapts and learns to apply, and the earliest cultivation method was born. Between one breath and one breath, Yin and Yang continue. Then evolved the Zhou Tian operation, the guidance of the spit. The inward and outward Qi is the small ZhouTian, and the big ZhouTian can communicate heaven and earth, heaven and man exchange, borrow the force of nature, and there are endless changes. \n\nThis book is written by Jiran, a strategist in the ChunQiu Period, which contains a variety of knowledge and philosophy from all over the world, and is one of the four sacred texts of Taoism. \n\nNote: Once you have fully studied one Initial approach book, the cultivatior will be bound to that Initial approach and will not be able to learn any other Initial approach! -->
  <RI_BookB.description>一本由灵气凝聚而成的古书，书名写着《性命真经》。\n\n内丹法门为所有法门之祖，无数功法神通都由内丹演变而来。灵气在体内沿着经脉循环往复，令身体逐渐适应，就诞生了最早的修炼法。一呼一吸之间，阴阳接续，之后演变出了周天运转，吐纳导引。灵气的内敛与外放乃是小周天，而大周天，则可以沟通天地。以我之灵气，合天地之造化。\n\n此书为内丹祖师——天云真人所撰写。\n\n注意：一旦彻底读完一本法门书，修炼者将与这条法门绑定，无法再学习其他法门！</RI_BookB.description>
  <!-- EN: After reading {PARENT_label}, the cultivator{STUDIER_labelShort} takes the Internal pellet Initial approach as his cultivation direction! -->
  <RI_BookB.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>阅读了{PARENT_label}后, 修炼者{STUDIER_labelShort}将内丹法门作为了自己的修炼方向！</RI_BookB.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: {PARENT_label} becomes some sparks of Qi and disappears. -->
  <RI_BookB.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterTitle>{PARENT_label}化为点点灵光，消散了。</RI_BookB.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterTitle>
  
  <!-- EN: Initial approach book-Physical -->
  <RI_BookC.label>炼体法门书《炼体录》</RI_BookC.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient book made of Qi condensation, the title of the book is "Cultivation of the KongFu skills."\n\nPhysical Initial approach is one of the oldest Initial approach, through boxing and kung fu, physical exercise, while strengthening the whole body's meridians and even the organ with Qi, turning itself into a sharp weapon that is indestructible. Entry needs to be cut hair for marrow, reborn, deep also have to open the meridian, five gas Chaoyuan, the whole body Qi operation freely, Cultivators do not hold the sword, can also break out a strong lethality. \n\nThis book is a martial arts book written by Cheng Zongyou, a famous martial artist in the late Ming Dynasty, which contains a large number of martial arts, cudgels, spears and knives. \n\nNote: Once you have fully studied one Initial approach book, the cultivatior will be bound to that Initial approach and will not be able to learn any other Initial approach! -->
  <RI_BookC.description>一本由灵气凝聚而成的古书，书名写着《炼体录》。\n\n炼体法门是最古老的法门之一，通过拳脚功夫，肉体锻炼，同时以灵气强化全身经脉乃至五脏六腑，将自身化为一尊锋利兵器。入门需得伐毛换髓，脱胎换骨，深入还得打通经脉，五气朝元，全身灵气运转自如，不持兵刃，也能爆发出极强的杀伤力。\n\n注意：一旦完全钻研完一本法门书，修炼者将与这条法门绑定，无法再学习其他法门！</RI_BookC.description>
  <!-- EN: After reading {PARENT_label}, the cultivator{STUDIER_labelShort} takes the Physical Initial approach as his cultivation direction! -->
  <RI_BookC.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>阅读了{PARENT_label}后, 修炼者{STUDIER_labelShort}将炼体法门作为了自己的修炼方向！</RI_BookC.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
